        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "It would be nice to have some level of automated coding standards compliance assistance, and below are a couple of options:\n\nMost likely this is too old and doesn't work with PHP 5.1.4: [phpCodeBeautifier|http:\/\/www.waterproof.fr\/products\/phpCodeBeautifier\/]\n(Thanks, [~gavin])\n\nTo evaluate: [PHP_CodeSniffer|http:\/\/matrix.squiz.net\/developer\/tools\/php_cs]\n(Thanks, [~nicklo])\n\n*Help Wanted* - We would like help with evaluating such a system for Zend Framework code, as we would possibly integrate a good solution as a pre-commit hook to the Subversion repository."
        },
